Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.59,0:22:41.04,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}時という波の音に いつかは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:48.44,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}紛れて 褪せてしまう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:56.28,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}「忘れたいとは思わないなら」と
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:23:03.48,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}告げた貴方は 残響を繋ぎあわせた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:11.23,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}ただ美しいままであれば構わないと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:19.00,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}白い脆い真実　それだけを求めても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:26.56,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}繕うことさえも適わない綻びを
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.43,0:23:33.76,EDJ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}痛む声が響く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:32.79,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}此时在心中细述的是记忆的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.59,0:22:41.04,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}曾几何时 冠以时光的浪花声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:48.44,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}相互交织 逐渐褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:56.28,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}「如果想要忘记的话 就是不会再思念」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.95,0:23:03.48,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}你写下的这句话 将余音紧紧相系
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.93,0:23:11.23,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}只要继续保持瑰丽便可
