Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.09,0:23:26.56,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}连修补都不被允许的绽线
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.43,0:23:33.76,EDZ,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be3\blur3\1vc(&H5C393D&,&H5C393D&,&HFFFFFF&,&HFFFFFF&)}痛苦的悲鸣缠绕耳边不断回荡
